					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210617063504/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/Agg">Aggeus</a></li>
					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210617063504/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/Zac">Zacharias</a></li>
					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210617063504/http://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/Mal">Malachias</a></li>
